[When you do things to protect yourself, such as eliminate standing water where mosquitoes breed, you are also helping to protect your horse. The best protection for your horse(s) is vaccination. It is effective and can be augmented by horse-approved mosquito repellant sprays.

Likely this disease will die out after a hard frost. - Mod.TG

